{"tid":778899,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有人疑不滿陳浩天於FCC演講 虛報FCC餐廳發生火警","createTime":"2018-08-14T04:41:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T07:14:51.000Z","uid":136994,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"62e8d870f465e0613381ea581e230e82a40b6379","tid":778899,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:41:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180814/58560493\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180814%2F58560493&d=8wRfes4BNiqzHQc1cLrktpUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=2df44d13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180814%2F58560493&h=49d58e5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180814/58560493</a><br />\n<br />\n香港外國記者會（FCC）邀請香港民族黨召集人陳浩天今日在午餐會演講，接連遭受外交部及建制陣營打壓。早前一度有消防員進入FCC會址，未幾撤退。消防處表示，今早約11時接報，指位於中環下亞厘畢道2號北座香港外國記者會的餐廳冒煙，消防員10分鐘後到場，經調查後發現屬惡意虛報，其後收隊離開。<br />\n<br />\n陳浩天演講於下午1時15分開始，親建制組織「珍惜群組」今早到FCC門外掛起橫額示威，警方在會場外駐重兵部署封路，大批中外傳媒到場採訪。據了解，陳浩天早於9時在抗議前抵達FCC，陳上午10時許在facebook公佈:「多謝各位關心，我已經喺FCC入面。」<br />\n<br />\n珍惜群組動員參與同心護港、聲討反華基地（FCC）行動，由中環港鐵站遊行到下亞厘畢道的FCC外抗議。珍惜群組展示橫額及高叫口號，指「港獨非常毒」，促政府收回會址，「掃賊清場」，以捍衛國家主權，又倡23條立法「降魔伏妖」，並要求FCC接抗議信。有市民成立反港獨街坊關注會。香港政研會、匯賢起動在FCC會場外，輪流以揚聲器高叫口號。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「保衛香港運動」十餘人今早亦由金鐘海富中心遊行至政府總部，抗議陳浩天被邀演講，質疑以新聞自由作平台為港獨宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n鳩嗚團、新民主同盟譚凱邦及馮志活牧師等人則發起多個民間團體到場聲援FCC，捍衛言論自由。據警方透露，聲援因沒事前申請，不會獲准進入FCC的公眾人士示威區。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">警察又唔拉人吖？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adeb93b2add11b809a31b4fc5518779d0876e205","tid":778899,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:43:12.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"b25cbb883a192773eceeefd18ce1a377b4db264d","tid":778899,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:43:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f416124a88f883f46a52375a667f9d78f14df7b8","tid":778899,"uid":192263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:04:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4bf78b4ea8d352155cf253ef3cc87b80544cc25","tid":778899,"uid":55913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:28:27.000Z","msg":"支那狗 係咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"295b010199aa3d19eb4f338b395646eb1d18c5a5","tid":778899,"uid":52276,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:52:51.000Z","msg":"集會前有冇向警方申請呀？非法集會？<br />\n吖，唔記得黑警盲撚曬添&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254abd801cb082b12fc4e8acf9cc0d906d50d3c0","tid":778899,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T06:22:11.000Z","msg":"浪費消防力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d186d05453fe9c54eb3e4d34000789f84326fa6","tid":778899,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T07:14:51.000Z","msg":"點解唔搵施x蟲座陣？"}]}